Enclosing class:
PluginAdapter
protected class PluginAdapter.SharedThreading
extends PluginAdapter.Threading

Shares a Thread with other SharedThreading plugins in the same agent.

There are two callbacks:

  • the subscription watcher, to track blackboard activity
  • the scheduler trigger, to request plugin_cycle()

The order is:
  1. the blackboard calls "subscriptionWatcher.signalNotify(..)"
  2. the subscription watcher calls "schedTrigger.trigger()"
  3. the scheduler calls "this.trigger()"
  4. "this.trigger()" calls "plugin_cycle()"
    5. .
